I've been working on one such story, though the waifur is a troodontid Latenovenatrix (with raven-like feather patterning). >Surviving in arid wastelands

>Fight for survival against raiders, vagabonds, warlords, marauders, and opportunists with just as little left to lose as you
>Stumble upon a small raiding party, three men strong, about to claim what looks like a choice heap of engine parts
>Overhear something about a weapons cache
>They're all leathery, sun-worn, toothless, and very much armed with hackneyed shanks and clubs at best
>-skip-

>She's injured and bleeding
